Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:12.85,Main,,0,0,0,,But the wish comes true,\Nnot for me, the Selector,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.47,Main,,0,0,0,,but instead for Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}, the LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...the truth behind these battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:51.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ambulance! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right! A phone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe has a cell with her! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:51.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:02:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:12.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:22.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"Staff Station"\NYup, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,The doctor said she's stable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup. I called already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,And, I... wanted to wait here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,until Hitoe's mom comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:03:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She is your friend. I'm sure\Nyou want to be next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:10.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll call if something comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You were right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have continued battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I won the battle, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...will become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,...Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:41.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She told me all about the Selectors,\NLRIGs, and Eternal Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She said that all girls\Nwho become LRIGs go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,So, even Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}and everyone else...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,White room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama? Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is this "Mayu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I only know her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}tricked me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear about LRIGs\Nreplacing the Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She's probably me\Nin the outside world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,She was saying how she would\Nhelp me with my wish all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,She must have been making fun of me--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzu--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:27.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--or, so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare she.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:33.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}... you're so horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIGs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,...are not allowed to share\Nthe truth with their Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you know all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?! What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,If this rule is broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,and the Selector learns\Nthe truth and declines to battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,that LRIG will forever lose\Ntheir chance to escape from the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You're trying to... do the same to Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,After that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Of all the people, I became Hitoe's LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I wondered what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Do I have to deceive Hitoe\Nso that she battles again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,If I didn't, I would never\Nbe able to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get along, okay, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you... know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That's just something I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if we were friends, we only\Nknew each other for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It looked like she did\Nforget about me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be your LRIG from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIG...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What is your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,If you have a wish,\NI can make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.48,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's make your wish come true, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yu... zu... ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go back outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I was to hurt Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki... I want to see Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:45.34,Main,,0,0,0,,So, can you tell me what your wish is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?! Hitoe? Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew she didn't have any wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I still needed to rely on my only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:19.04,Main,,0,0,0,,...just when I thought I had to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?! Does it hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you going through this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,it's probably because it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...have... a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I want... friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,After all the suffering she went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:18.18,Main,,0,0,0,,After all the pain she went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,She still asked for the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I want... friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That was it, seeing her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:56.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true when they say that\Nyou can't go against a girl's tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish... Hitoe's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wishes which could only\Ncome true at the sacrifice of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nhad to go through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}was lost,\Nand in pain like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,After that, I started thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You want your wish to come true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go out and battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:49.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I had her battle you, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.36,Main,,0,0,0,,And then I spoke the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I was hoping Hitoe would remove herself\Nfrom battle after knowing the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if that happened, you would be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:10.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to sacrifice\NHitoe just to get back outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:16.22,Main,,0,0,0,,And anyway, if I can't\Nlive as Yuzuki Kurebayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,If I can't love Kazuki\Nas Yuzuki Kurebayashi anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...it makes no sense for me to be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... Where's Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, it looks like she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,She's calmed down now...\NThe doctor is keeping watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,She was so sweet, but I\Ndon't know what's in her mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,She scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know... I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What... should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, come over to my house tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I made her battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:47.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But... you did it for Hitoe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Being able to do something for others...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I think that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go. This would be the\Nsecond time you've stayed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Before going...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.79,Main,,0,0,0,,...can I ask you one favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this okay? Can you see clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,My, Yuzuki-{\i1}chan {\i0}and Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.\NAre you both stepping out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Just going to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's going to snow, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cornerstone"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be your girlfriend, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,This is about the only time\Nwe can be together as lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Dad and Mom are at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone else is at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,If we only have one umbrella
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,it won't look strange being together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's snowing... Kazuki, it's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You were always like that, even before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You always led me... protected me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I've loved you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.65,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll protect you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I am your lover after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:16.64,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,She made my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.53,Main,,0,0,0,,...Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzu... ki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"Send Complete"\NSo, all prepared and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll come for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You and that girl only have\Nbattles in your minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything else is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You both really are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:23.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to sacrifice\NHitoe just to get back outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:33.68,Main,,0,0,0,,She made my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:54.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You see these?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,It started to snow, so I need\Nto wipe the potatoes dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,didn't have any wish\Nof wanting to do--or be--something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't really care about\Nhaving friends or not, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...or, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I made friends.\NI was happy, and it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be with them as long as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I do anything for my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma's happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You are Ru-{\i1}chan {\i0}after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Where should I put these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you put them over there\Nwhere they can be under the sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you were a normal girl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you were like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what your wish--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama don't know... Don't know!\NI don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama didn't know! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama didn't know at all\Nthat Selectors and LRIGs switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying! It's true, Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to just battle together with Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course. You're my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Good night, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure I did. It's Iona's fan event, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what she means by "select"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It must be about choosing something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder where it's being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.43,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:11.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that? I sent a message,\Nbut I got nothing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Search... Do a search on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona... "fan event"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,"Iona fan event"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,"Urazoe Iona, fan event.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Urazoe Iona Fan Event"\NA message to those who select...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.47,Main,,0,0,0,,To those who are forced to select...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,To those who do not refuse to select..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,"Those who select"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She's calling out to Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"Urazoe Iona"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really close by...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to speak to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...going to battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.09,0:23:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a wish now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.76,0:23:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Summer of Dreams."
